801/* Analog to Digital Converter (ADC) */
802/* */
803/******************************************************************************/
804
805/*
806 * @brief Specific device feature definitions (not present on all devices in the STM32F0 serie)
807 */
808#define ADC_CHANNEL_VBAT_SUPPORT
810/******************** Bits definition for ADC_ISR register ******************/
811#define ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Pos (0U)
812#define ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Pos)
813#define ADC_ISR_ADRDY ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Msk
814#define ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Pos (1U)
815#define ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Pos)
816#define ADC_ISR_EOSMP ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Msk
817#define ADC_ISR_EOC_Pos (2U)
818#define ADC_ISR_EOC_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOC_Pos)
819#define ADC_ISR_EOC ADC_ISR_EOC_Msk
820#define ADC_ISR_EOS_Pos (3U)
821#define ADC_ISR_EOS_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOS_Pos)
822#define ADC_ISR_EOS ADC_ISR_EOS_Msk
823#define ADC_ISR_OVR_Pos (4U)
824#define ADC_ISR_OVR_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_OVR_Pos)
825#define ADC_ISR_OVR ADC_ISR_OVR_Msk
826#define ADC_ISR_AWD1_Pos (7U)
827#define ADC_ISR_AWD1_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_AWD1_Pos)
828#define ADC_ISR_AWD1 ADC_ISR_AWD1_Msk
830/* Legacy defines */
831#define ADC_ISR_AWD (ADC_ISR_AWD1)
832#define ADC_ISR_EOSEQ (ADC_ISR_EOS)
